         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <ab>Sacred to the Shades of the Dead.  Augustus Veranus centurian of the second praetorian cohort heir of the well deserving Marcus Augustus Januarius horseman, centurion of the 9th praetorian cohort Faventinius, who lived 20 years and performed three years and nine months of military service.</ab>
